high_descs: Go forward and turn to the left to face the table.
Pick the ladle up from the table.
Turn around and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the ladle up again.
Back up and face the lowest drawer to the right of the sink.
Put the ladle in the lowest drawer to the right of the sink and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a ladle in a drawer.

high_descs: Head to the wall and turn left to face the side of the wooden table.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle to the right of the apple on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the spoon inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk forward and turn around to face the drawers to the right of the sink.
Open the bottom drawer to the right of the sink, put the rinsed spoon inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spoon in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left to face the wooden table.
Pick up the largest metal spoon from the table.
Turn around to face the sink.
Rinse off the spoon in the sink.
Turn to face the cabinets below the sink.
Put the spoon in the third drawer down to the right of the sink, underneath the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a wooden spoon to put it in the third cabinet down on the right of the sink.
